Sample_source_name_ch1: clear cell renal cell carcinoma cell line
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: The 786-O cell line was purchased from the ATCC. Cells were grown in RPMI 1640 medium supplemented with 10% (v/v) fetal bovine serum. Cells with stable PBRM1 knockdown were produced using  MISSION Lentiviral Transduction Particles  purchased from Sigma-Aldrich (clone IDs: TRCN0000235890 and TRCN0000015994; sh1 and sh2, respectively) and used according to the manufacturer’s instructions. Briefly, 1x10^5 cells were transduced with the viral particles at a MOI
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: 150,000 cells were harvested, tagmented with 5 μL Nextera Tn5 Transposes from Nextera kit (Illumina) for 30 min, amplified up to 13 cycles and purified., Purified libraries were size selected on 2% agarose gel (150-700bp). Libraries were sequenced on Illumina Hi-Seq2500 (40 bp paired-end).
Sample_data_processing: Reads were trimmed for Illumina adapter sequences using in-house scripts and aligned to the GRCh37/hg19 using Bowtie2 (version 2.1.0) with parameters –S –X 2000. Reads that align to mtDNA, with quality value Q<30, as well as duplicated reads, were discarded using in-house scripts and Samtools. Coverage tracks were generated using deepTools bamCoverage with parameters –normalizeUsingRPKM –binsize 10.
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: bigWIg coverage tracks were generated using deepTools bamCoverage with parameters –normalizeUsingRPKM –binsize 10. The bed files represent significant peaks.
